  "Description": {
    "English": "An attachment for the Multi-Tool <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scanner</span> that allows the device to detect and decode the cloaking signal of nearby Autophage units.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> to activate the Scanner. As its detector waveform passes over the local area, it will <span class=\"name name-stellar\">automatically reveal</span> any <span class=\"name name-stellar\">nearby Autophage entities</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "多用途工具<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>的配件，允许设备侦测并破译附近自噬体单元的隐身信号。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>激活扫描仪。当扫描装置的波形经过本地区域，<span class=\"name name-stellar\">周遭的所有自噬体实体</span>都将被<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自动揭示</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工具組<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描器</span>的配件，能讓裝置偵測並破譯附近自噬單位的隱形訊號。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 啟動掃描器。偵測器波形經過當地區域時，會<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自動顯示</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">附近任何自噬存在體</span>。"
  },
